<div n="a" subtype="fragment" type="textpart"><ab> 
    <lb n="1"/><supplied reason="lost">Φιλωνίδης τῶι πατρὶ χαίρειν.</supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>

    <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="3"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="4"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><app type="editorial"><lem><supplied reason="lost">χ</supplied>ρόνον</lem><rdg resp="Mahaffy"><gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="6" unit="character"/>νον</rdg></app> ἔχων <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="5"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>αις, οὕτω γὰρ <supplied reason="lost">ἔστα</supplied>ι τυχεῖν καὶ τὸν

    <lb n="6"/><app type="editorial"><lem resp="Clarysse">ἐπίλοιπον χρόνον</lem><rdg resp="Mahaffy"><supplied reason="lost">ὕστερον χ</supplied>ρόνον</rdg></app> εὐιλάτου τοῦ βασιλ<supplied reason="lost">έως. ο</supplied><unclear>ὐ</unclear> μὴν οὐθὲν ἐμοὶ

    <lb n="7"/><supplied reason="lost">ἔσται</supplied> <app type="editorial"><lem>μεῖζον</lem><rdg resp="Mahaffy"><supplied reason="lost">με</supplied>ῖζον</rdg></app> ἢ σοῦ προστατῆσα<supplied reason="lost">ι</supplied> <app type="editorial"><lem><supplied reason="lost">τὸν</supplied> <unclear>ἐπ</unclear>ίλοιπον</lem><rdg resp="Mahaffy"><supplied reason="lost">τον σου</supplied> λοιπὸν</rdg><rdg resp="Wilcken"><supplied reason="lost">τὸν</supplied> ἐ<supplied reason="lost">π</supplied>ί<supplied reason="lost">λοιπον</supplied></rdg></app> βίον, ἀξίως

    <lb n="8"/><supplied reason="lost">μὲ</supplied>ν σοῦ, <app type="editorial"><lem resp="Wilcken">ἀξίως δ’ ἐμοῦ</lem><rdg resp="Mahaffy">ἀξιῶς δέ μου</rdg></app>, καὶ ἐάν τι τῶν κατ’ ἄνθρωπον γίνηται,

    <lb n="9"/>τυχεῖν σε πάντων τῶν καλῶν. ὃ ἐμοὶ <supplied reason="lost">μ</supplied>έγιστον ἔσται <choice><reg>καλῶς</reg><orig>καλλῶς</orig></choice> σου

    <lb n="10"/>προστατῆσαι καὶ ζῶντός σου καὶ εἰς θεοὺς ἀπελθόντος. μάλιστα

    <lb n="11"/>μὲν οὖν τὴν πᾶσαν σπουδὴν πόησαι <app type="editorial"><lem><unclear>το</unclear>ῦ</lem><rdg resp="Mahaffy"><supplied reason="lost">το</supplied>ῦ</rdg></app> ἀφεθῆναί σε διὰ τέλους, 

    <lb n="12"/>εἰ δ’ ἄρα μὴ ὁρᾶις ὂν δυνατόν, αὐτήν <app type="editorial"><lem resp="Wilcken">γ<supplied reason="lost">ε τὴ</supplied>ν</lem><rdg resp="Mahaffy"><supplied reason="lost">περὶ τὴ</supplied>ν</rdg><rdg resp="Wilamowitz"><supplied reason="lost">κατὰ τὴ</supplied>ν</rdg><rdg resp="Van Beek"><note xml:lang="en">also vielleicht <expan><ex>κατ’</ex></expan> αὐτήν γ<supplied reason="lost">ε τὴ</supplied>ν</note></rdg></app> ἀνα<supplied reason="lost">χώ</supplied>ρησιν τοῦ

    <lb n="13"/>ποταμοῦ, καθ’ ὃν χρόνον οὐθείς ἐστιν κίνδυνος, ἀ<supplied reason="lost">λλ’ ἐ</supplied>ξέσται καὶ

    <lb n="14"/>Θεύδωρον καταλειφθέντα ταὐτὸ <choice><reg>ποιεῖν</reg><orig>ποεῖν</orig></choice>, ὅπως τ<supplied reason="lost">οῦτό</supplied>ν γε

    <lb n="15"/>τὸν χρόνον παρεπιδημῆις. τοῦτο <add place="above">δ’</add> ἔχε τῆι δια<supplied reason="lost">νοία</supplied>ι, ὅτι

    <lb n="16"/>οὐθέν σοι <unclear>μ</unclear>ὴ γενηθῆι λυπηρόν, ἀλλὰ πᾶν ἐ<supplied reason="lost">μοὶ ἔστ</supplied>αι πεφρον

    <lb n="17" break="no"/>τισμένον τοῦ σὲ γενέσθαι ἄλυπον. <space extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <app type="editorial"><lem><supplied reason="lost">ἔρρωσο.</supplied></lem><rdg resp="von Wilamowitz"><supplied reason="lost">εὐτύχει</supplied></rdg><rdg resp="Witkowski"><supplied reason="lost">ἔρρωσο</supplied></rdg></app>
